name: GoogleDinoRun
description:
THE GOOGLE DINO 2.0 CAN MAKES YOU BRRRRRRRRRRRR

Well, actually this game is not yet complete, it's still in the early stages. The whole game demo ends when you reach a score of 57,000 points. (Of course, you can keep playing...);

Also, I have completely run out of ideas for new bosses. If you see and play this game, please help me come up with some new boss ideas! The game is very difficult overall, with a default life value of 100 bars, and a settings interface will be added in the future. 

I haven't created an ending screen for the demo, because I'm lazy. So, good luck to you!
